narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Connections between elliptic curves and modular forms

I learned a lot! The main topics were elliptic curves, modular forms, and the Hecke algebra, but we saw how to embed any torus in the complex projective plane using the Weierstrass function, how to calculate the dimension of the space of modular forms for any weight using line bundles and talked about the Langlands correspondence.
